data.description: Welcome Home! You will love this home that features 3 bedrooms 1.5 baths. Inviting Foyer as soon as you enter. Updates include Kitchen, bathroom, 2020 flooring throughout & carpet, 2021 Roof & Garage door, 2024 New Carpet on Stairs, 2024 French Drain, 2024 Painted Garage interior walls and floor. The Garage is partially converted which could be a great Workout Room or playroom. Don't miss the large back yard for entertaining & watching the dogs or children at play.
